---
<!-- <main class=""> -->
			
    <div class="flex flex-row space-x-4 mx-auto py-12 container">
        <div class="font-mono">
            <div class="p-8">
                <h2 class="font-extrabold text-teal-400 underline deocoration-indigo-500 text-2xl">{SITE_TITLE}</h2>
                <h1 class="text-stone-400">I am a software developer and recent graduate</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 w-full text-stone-400">
                <p>I'm a Mexican citizen ðŸ‡²ðŸ‡½ that used to live in the US ðŸ‡ºðŸ‡¸. 
                Currently back in my home country.
