                with JS, React, Java, C, and Python. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- basis-full for image  -->  
        <div class="pt-24">
            <img class="animate-zoom-in-slow rounded-full border border-dotted scale-150" src='/assets/alfonso2.png'  />
